      <title>减税 6 亿美元后，硅谷银行金融债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/svb-financial-bonds-rise-after-600-million-cut-to-tax-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[硅谷银行金融集团（SVB Financial Group）的潜在税负获得了超过 6 亿美元的减免，增加了一些与硅谷银行（Silicon Valley Bank）破产前母公司相关的债券，并消除了其根据破产法第 11 章偿还债权人的障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/svb-financial-bonds-rise-after-600-million-cut-to-tax-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 16:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
