    <item>
      <title>雷诺承诺采用新工艺将电动汽车电池成本降低 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/renault-vows-to-lower-ev-battery-costs-20-with-cheaper-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷诺公司承诺将电池成本降低约 20%，以通过采用更便宜的电池化学成分和新的电动汽车零部件生产工艺来保持竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/renault-vows-to-lower-ev-battery-costs-20-with-cheaper-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚：法国罢工使炼油厂运营复杂化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/exxon-says-strike-disrupts-operations-at-its-french-oil-refinery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司表示，其位于法国北部的格拉旺雄炼油厂发生罢工，导致该厂的燃料生产复杂化，并重申该工厂面临停工的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/exxon-says-strike-disrupts-operations-at-its-french-oil-refinery</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
